release_note: Access to Community is now restricted to users who are 18 at the start of the calendar year.

We have integrated an online forum: MindShift CBT Community. The MindShift CBT Community Forum allows users to interact with and support each other on their journeys coping with anxiety. The Terms of Use and Privacy Policy have also been updated to reflect this new feature.
